My team is trying to start using PathWeaver, I’m having a problem with the code deployed from the System Id Tool. In the deploy log, it says “SSH connection to 172.22.11.2 failed”. Also, the RioLog in VS Code says:

*********** Robot program starting **********

  • Camera Server Library Not Found
  • NT: could not open persistent file ‘/home/lvuser/networktables.json’: No such file or directory
  • NT: Listening on NT3 port 1735, NT4 port 5810
  • Initializing logger
  • Read JSON
  • Setup motors
  • Setup SPARK MAX (Brushed)

I have already updated my software, Roborio, and SparkMax’s to the latest version (2023). I also tried using a blank template of code on the Roborio, but it made no difference.
